## Limitations
The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in sources that either support or oppose animal testing. Additionally, ethical considerations are inherently subjective, and cultural differences may influence perspectives on the issue. The report does not cover all possible alternatives to animal testing, focusing instead on the ethical debate.